body.description: Owls, birds, hearts and flowers make the Everything Kids hoot hoot 4 piece toddler set a whimsical choice for your little girl's bedroom. Whimsical hearts, playful flowers, and a sweet owl and hedgehog come together for a bright, happy bedding collection. The Everything Kids hoot hoot 4 piece toddler bedding set is made from extra soft microfiber fabrics. The convenient 4 piece set includes a printed comforter, flat top sheet, fitted bottom sheet, and a printed pillowcase. Designed to fit a standard toddler size bed, with a 28 x 52" mattress.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Everything Kids Hoot Hoot Pink, Aqua, Green and White 4 Piece Toddler Bed Set - Comforter, Fitted Bottom Sheet, Flat Top Sheet, Reversible Pillowcase Wise owls, hedgehogs & fun flowers make the Everything Kids Hoot Hoot 4 Piece Toddler Bed Set a whimsical choice for your little girls bedroom! reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 6, 2017
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars We LOVE this bedding set
reviews.reviewText: We LOVE this bedding set! The colors are SO vibrant and the comforter is fairly thick in comparison to my other daughter's set. My daughter always looks so comfy in her bed with this set! Would definitely purchase again!!!**Update:Almost 2 years after purchasing this set, I wouldn’t change the 5 star rating! I still absolutely love this set. Every time I put this set in our daughter’s bed, it makes me smile lol!We are going on the third child to use this set, and it is still as awesome as when we bought it! The color is still SUPER vibrant and the comforter is soft and still as plush as when it was brand new (just keep in mind it IS a toddler set, so when I say plush, I’m not comparing to a queen/king size plush comforter. I’m comparing it to another toddler bedding set we purchased. This one FAR EXCEEDS the softness/plushness of the other set!). If you’re looking for a really cute, bright toddler set with owls, give this a try!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2018
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It doesn't smell bad like chemicals and it feels like regular sheets should ...
reviews.reviewText: Bought it twice so I have a spare. Real talk, it's the cheapest toddler bedding set on amazon, ebay, or wish. It's not hideous. It doesn't smell bad like chemicals and it feels like regular sheets should feel, smooth/soft. My toddler was very excited to have her "big girl blanket". It's not really my style but I figure I can buy a duvet cover and the other stuff even cheaper later on and right now she has two sets of this for $40. A comforter alone typically costs that much. 10/10 cheap and decent.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 16, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Cute, but as a mom of three, I'm disappointed.
reviews.reviewText: Lets start off with the positive.Its cute. It is. The colors are cheerful and bright. It matches her room, and she really likes it!However. The comforter is very thin. Almost like two sheets of fabric sewn together. I have not washed it yet, so I dont know how it will wash, but if you order this, just remember this review. It is thin. If I had to buy it again, I wouldn't spend more than $20 for it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2017
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent and cute toddler bedding set
reviews.reviewText: My husband and I bought this bedding set as a present for our daughter with hopes that it would encourage her to stay in her new toddler bed once we transitioned her out of the crib. This product has exceeded my expectations. It is super cute, my daughter loves it, sheets feel nice and soft and the comforter is the perfect thickness and not super heavy. The product has maintained its quality and appearance since being washed a few times already. I would definitely recommend this bedding set to people.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 27, 2021
reviews.reviewText: This feels like a down blanket. It is the softest of 4 blanket set I purchased. The design is cute. My only concern is how it will hold up after washed a few times. It is the perfect summer blanket.Edit:It has been over a year and the blanket has endured plenty of washes. I highly recommend this blanket, especially for summer!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 22, 2016
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very please with this purchase!
reviews.reviewText: I just got this set for my granddaughter's toddler bed at our house. I am thrilled! The whole set is so soft and cozy feeling. I washed all of the pieces before making the bed on gentle cycle and delicate for the drying. Every piece came out beautifully and I know when she arrives in a few days, she's going to love her bedding as much as me. The bed spread IS thin as some other customers mentioned, but it's just thick enough. Perfect and so cute.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 12, 2017
reviews.reviewText: My daughter loves this bedding set. It comes with a flat sheet, fitted sheet, pillowcase and a comforter. One side of the comforter has owls and animals on it, and the other is plainer -- just shapes, basically. It's very cute, and fits with her room really well. The comforter isn't heavy at all, so it wouldn't be good for cold houses; but we live in Tennessee and keep our house fairly warm so it's perfect. Just heavy enough to keep her warm, but not so heavy as to make her hot. (She runs hot anyway, so something too heavy wouldn't work.)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 13, 2016
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars She immediately fell in love with everything about the comforter
reviews.reviewText: My husband and I decided to switch our two year old daughter to a toddler bed, we thought that a new comforter set would help that transition. She immediately fell in love with everything about the comforter, fitted sheet and pillowcase. She loves owls and just points at each one and says owl, owl owl! We didn't know if she was ready for a full size pillow but it has ended up working out great, we bought a very flat pillow, and with it being full size her head didn't fall off of it during the night like it normally did with her toddler pillow.Another positive, the sheets and comforter are all incredibly soft, and the comforter is the perfect density, it isn't too thick or too thin. After washing everything remained just as soft, the comforter didn't bunch at all afterwards.Would definitely buy again, and when she moves on to a twin bed we will definitely buy from this company.
A mi niña le gusto mucho!!

reviews.reviewTitle: Great quality set for excellent price
reviews.reviewText: We are very happy with the quality of this bed set. We ordered it for our toddler and it fits her little toddler bed perfectly, with some room to spare. The fabric is soft. The comforter is fluffy and reminds us of a duvet. The colours are bright and the pattern is adorable. Our daughter loves it. We are really happy with the quality and you cannot beat the price. Other 4 piece sets are going for double or triple this price. Excellent quality set for a fraction of the cost.
I got an open box deal so was happier with the reduced price. Overall good quality and very cute!

El diseño esta muy bonito pero no le quedó al colchón de la cuna de mi hija y se supone que es el tradicional asi es que solo estamos usando la sabana y el edredon, si lo van a comprar asegurense de convertir las medidas de pulgadas a centimetros y midan bien su colchón...

We got this set for our toddler's transition to a big girl bed. She loved the designs and the option to flip the blanket either way. Only complaint is that the duvet didn't remain tucked under her mattress so she would get up several times a night due to being cold with the blanket not on her. Had to put a larger duvet on her bed.
